    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new but without that heavy new-car price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to love it!",
