    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo is a textbook example of the A80 platform's engineering excellence. Under the hood, the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six retains its factory sequential twin-turbocharged configuration, delivering linear power through the robust Getrag V160 six-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, supported by a factory-spec double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Every component, from the four-piston braking system to the original intercooler piping, exhibits zero thermal fatigue or oxidation. This is a collector-grade specimen with flawless mechanical synchronization and a pristine undercarriage.",
